title: AI_Emoji_Kitchen_Lab
description: 这是一个基于深度学习的表情符号（Emoji）融合项目，旨在于通过大模型实现Google Emoji Kitchen风格的表情符号融合，能够将两个不同的emoji融合成一个全新的、富有创意的emoji图像。

title: PDF_Summary_Tool

title: TeX-QB-Gen
description: Generate question banks directly from textbooks.  Leverage OpenRouter's multimodal/text models and local OCR capabilities to extract math problems and solutions from images, web pages, or PDFs, and generate uniformly formatted TeX question banks.
